    <abstract>
      <para>This manual documents the interfaces of the xmlsec
      library. For a tutorial and usage examples, see the
      <ulink url="../tutorial/index.html">XML Security Library Tutorial</ulink>.
      </para>
    </abstract>
  </bookinfo>

